short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The extension optimizes daily work when adding freight - it automatically sends orders for cargo transportation.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The new version of the extension is intended for mixed and transport companies to speed up the search for suitable orders. Search for orders simultaneously on multiple sites.
